data.description: Look no more, this is what you are looking for and more! Gorgeous, spacious executive home on a quiet cul de sac. Welcome home to this 2 story, 4BD 2.5BA house, over 3600 square feet of living space. The first floor has  a large dining room, living room, huge upgraded Kitchen with granite counters and custom backsplash installed in 2019,42-inch cabinets, Wolf Gas Range, center island, Kenmore Elite refrigerator and dishwasher, and a large pantry (7.5 X 7.0) with custom lighting.The kitchen overlooks the family room which has a wood burning fireplace. Upstairs you will find 4 larg Bed rooms. The Master BD has a sitting room, perfect for a nursery or office, his (ELFA) and her custom walk-in closets, (12 X 8) and (11 X 9). The Master Bath has a Jacuzzi tub, separate shower stall and dual sinks. One BD is equipped with a California closet. Go downstairs to the Finished basement, it has a French drain with 2 sump pumps, new expansion tank, newer HVAC system, rough in plumbing for an 8 X 5 bathroom, studs, rock, up flush basin, drain pipes, concrete floor, and a 3 X 5 closet. All wood shelving will be staying. Go out side and be amazed with this POLE BARN (30 X 40), this could be conducive for a contractor or small business owner. There are 12-foot ceilings, 10 X 16 wide insulated garage door, 10-foot overhang, gas line 1 1/4 “with its own meter, 100-amp service, outlets every 8’ on their own 20-amp breaker, Lift master garage door with WIFI battery backup,2” pipe from house as spare, 2” pipe from house main breaker for power. There is a large wolf composite deck (42 X 20), perfect for entertaining, a whole house generator so you never have to worry about losing electricity! Established fruit trees (peach, pear & apple) and raspberries. The2-car attached garage has a new lift master garage opener and custom-built loft shelving. There is a 6-zone sprinkler system, and the front yard has EP Henry tombstone pavers around the flower beds. This house backs to a State land, nothing can be built behind the home for added privacy. Solar panels (42) $117/mth. A must see house with no doubt, move in ready.
